spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 2.3 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 110,378  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)
Use: Warrior be nimble, Warrior be quick. Warrior invoke the power of the candlestick to increase movement speed by 20% and Haste by 6,531 for 20 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Taking damage greater than 25% of your health grants you 2,602 Avoidance and increases healing taken by 10% for 10 sec. This effect may only occur every 90 sec.

Falling damage reduced.
